{"article_id":"oqNbMkxxTzjqVRve","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Senate Democrats appear willing to use your paycheck","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"to play political hardball on taxes","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"unless Republicans agree to President Obama 's plan","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"to raise taxes on America 's top earners .","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"A top Senate Democrat warned Monday","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"that ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"if Republicans do n't relent ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"her caucus is willing to let all the Bush-era tax rates expire at the end of the year","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"-- in effect threatening to let the country fall off what many in Washington call the `` fiscal cliff . '' That cliff is approaching at the start of 2013 ,","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"when the Bush tax cuts are set to expire","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"and billions of dollars in automatic spending cuts","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"-- spawned by last summer 's debt-ceiling debate --","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"are set to take effect .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Lawmakers on both sides of the aisle are hoping to shift around those spending cuts","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"to spare key areas like defense ,","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"and to temporarily extend the Bush tax rates for at least some Americans .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"Some have warned","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"a failure","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"to do so","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"could send the nation back into recession .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"But Sen. Patty Murray , D-Wash. , indicated","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Democrats are willing to let the deadline pass","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"in order to better their negotiating position .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"`` So","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"if we ca n't get a good deal , a balanced deal","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"that calls on the wealthy to pay their fair share ,","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"then I will absolutely continue this debate into 2013","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"rather than lock in a long-term deal this year","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"that throws middle-class families under the bus , ''","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"she said in an address Monday afternoon at the Brookings Institution .","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"Murray is head of the Democratic Senatorial Campaign Committee , the campaign arm for Senate Democrats .","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"In the remarks , Murray explained","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"if all the tax cuts expire ,","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"then that will diminish the GOP argument","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"that the Democratic plan is tantamount to a tax hike","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"-- because come 2013 , any change to the tax code would be a tax cut . `` We will have a new fiscal and political reality , ''","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"Murray said .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"`` If the Bush tax cuts expire ,","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"every proposal will be a tax cut proposal","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"and the pledge","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"( to not raise taxes )","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"will no longer keep Republicans boxed in and unable to compromise .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"`` If middle-class families start seeing more money","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"coming out of their paychecks next year","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"-- are Republicans really going to stand up","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"and fight for new tax cuts for the rich ?","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"Are they going to continue opposing the Democrats ' middle-class tax cut","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"once the slate has been wiped clean ?","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"I think","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"they know","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"that that would be an untenable political position .","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"And I hope","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"this pushes them to come to the table with real revenue now","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"before being forced to the table","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"if we do n't get a deal before the New Year , ''","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"she said .","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"Murray added","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"that she hopes","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"`` it does n't come to that , ''","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"and that she 's seen `` encouraging signs ''","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"that Republicans are ready to deal .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"The political strategy underscores how heated the debate over the Bush tax cuts has become ,","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"and how risky it is for the American people .","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"President Obama is pushing for an extension of the rates only for American households","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"making less than $ 250,000 ,","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"and a tax hike for those","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"earning more than that .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Obama 's Democratic allies in Congress only want to pass that partial , one-year extension .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"Republicans only want to pass an extension","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"that continues those rates for everyone .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"Each side is accusing the other of threatening to trigger tax hikes in 2013 .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"Murray ,","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"while openly making that threat in her speech Monday ,","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"also preemptively argued","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"that Republicans would be to blame","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"if that happens .","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"She also suggested","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"if Republicans do n't negotiate to her party 's liking on the automatic spending cuts","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"-- known in Washington as the `` sequestration '' --","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"set to take effect at the start of next year ,","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"her party would let those cuts happen , too .","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"`` So anyone","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"who tells you","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"sequestration is going to simply disappear","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"because both sides want to avoid it","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"is either fooling themselves ,","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"or trying to fool you .","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"It is going to have to be replaced ,","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"and that replacement is going to have to be balanced , ''","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"Murray said .","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"Republicans claim","depth":5},{"id":93,"text":"Democrats are the ones","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"standing in the way of relief for millions of Americans .","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"In Republicans ' weekly radio address , Sen . Rob Portman , R-Ohio , accused Obama of pushing a tax hike","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"that will hurt employment .","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"`` Raising taxes on employers and the middle class , growing government at the expense of free enterprise ,","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"piling on new regulations","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"that increase the cost of doing business","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"-- these burdens make it harder , not easier , to create jobs in America , ''","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"`` Today ,","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"instead of lifting the burden on job creators ,","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"the President is once again calling for a massive tax increase on nearly 1 million small businesses","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"that employ tens of millions of Americans .","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"I guess","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"he still thinks","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"the private sector is doing just fine .","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"Well , the private sector is not fine .","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"And raising taxes on job creators during a jobs shortage makes about as much sense","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"as cutting off the water supply during a drought . ''","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"But Democratic Party leadership is apparently onboard with Murray 's plan .","depth":4},{"id":113,"text":"Adam Jentleson , spokesman for Senate Democratic Leader Harry Reid , told Fox Business Network","depth":5},{"id":114,"text":"that the majority leader has `` always said","depth":6},{"id":115,"text":"that we 're not changing anything","depth":7},{"id":116,"text":"until Republicans compromise","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"and embrace a plan","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"that includes revenues . ''","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":237,"left":122,"right":236,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":122,"left":120,"right":121,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":236,"left":209,"right":235,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":209,"left":148,"right":208,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":130,"right":147,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":4,"right":129,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":129,"left":124,"right":128,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":5,"right":123,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":123,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":128,"left":8,"right":127,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":9,"right":126,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":126,"left":125,"right":12,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":125,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":136,"right":146,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":136,"left":13